{"tid":1915984,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（香討）問：班建制大禍臨頭各自飛 同林鄭割席 都係投白票算","createTime":"2020-03-08T15:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T17:34:43.000Z","uid":201464,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"35f1315ad2cd52e87baf42df4898bd0613f391b5","tid":1915984,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:03:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28289423&amp;extra=&amp;page=5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D28289423%26extra%3D%26page%3D5&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=dafc94f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28289423&amp;extra=&amp;page=5</a><br />\n答：<br />\n<blockquote>絕對唔會投收黑金反對派！</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>建制派不是好東西，<br />\n但泛民比佢仲衰不知幾多倍！<br />\n永遠破壞無建設，<br />\n洗學生腦，<br />\n破壞法治，<br />\n唯有投建制！</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>只有兩個選擇&quot;<br />\n1.投建制<br />\n2.唔投票</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>泛民強勢，我鍾意鋤強扶弱，所以投建制一票</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>投黃黑對家係天經地義！寧要蠢建制，唔要黃黑狗</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>更加要投啦</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>只知一定唔投犯民,其餘睇下點先</blockquote><br />\n呢方面 香討大半年前都識得諗過依家班連登仔 好心連登仔學下嘢啦"},{"pid":"a26d4831dacac95e3b646f5bf6499fdc63f77fa7","tid":1915984,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"74e4cac581092987eedc80f3d26e6163dac2483f","tid":1915984,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"a217a826f755a818de722942d602a26517b62a55","tid":1915984,"uid":53498,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"身為撐特首嘅一份子,建制唔妥柒婆即係唔妥我！一票不投偽建制！寧投黃黑泛民攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49377861c89cd4488a553eeb4617421f707f229e","tid":1915984,"uid":20